item.title: 2022-Jan-4: Meeting Minutes and Attachments
item.description: This is information from our Zoom call today. Please take a moment to look it over before Thursday’s meeting at the Wieting at 5 p.m. Denise —– Forwarded Message —– From: “Jon D Werger” WergerJ@wellmark.com To: “ldfletcher” ldfletcher@mchsi.com Sent: Tuesday, January 4, 2022 1:56:01 PM Subject: Healthy Hometown information Denise, Thank you for hosting today’s call, I enjoyed learning more about Toledo and Tama and the work you are doing.
